title: Implemented Location-Awareness via Google Play Location Services within the HomeActivity
message:
Implemented Location-Awareness via Google Play Location Services within the HomeActivity
 - Made a LocationAwareActivity to handle the GoogleApiServices connection handling and LocationRequests
 - Implementing activities just override onConnected to start tracking on startup, or manually call startLocationUpdatesWithChecks, and override onLocationChanged
